snippet.title: Maths Skills: Proof by Contradiction
snippet.description:
We discuss the idea of proof by contradiction and work through a small example - to prove that there is no smallest positive rational number.
Another useful dose of Maths for everyone by Dr Sarada Herke.

For more in-depth videos check out my Graph Theory channel
http://youtube.com/drsaradaherke
